Brent Name Meaning in English

What does the name Brent mean? What is the meaning of the name Brent, lucky number, lucky stone, origin and religion.

Brent is an Old English place name and surname. The place name can be from Celtic words meaning "holy one" (if it refers to the River Brent), or "high place", literally, "from a steep hill" (if it refers to the villages in Somerset and Devon, England) (Mills 1991).

Brent Name Meaning, Origin & Details

Meaning: Hill top Details: From the English surname which is from the Celtic meaning "steep hill".
